      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUTLAND SNICKERS (1) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (20.39) at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. TWO ODD SOCKS (2) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at this track over 340m behind Theo The Great (20.42) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can do much better this time. TAMARAMA BEACH (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (18.98) in a Grade 5 at Dubbo. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Cannot be underestimated. TRALEE TINY (7) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
